text: Bray-Saint Aignan is a French commune. It is in the department of Loiret. The municipality was created on 1 January 2017 and consists of the former communes of Bray-en-Val (the seat) and Saint-Aignan-des-Gués.Arrêté préfectoral 25 July 2016 == References == Category:2017 establishments in France Category:Communes in Loiret
title: Bray-Saint Aignan
